1
00:00:11,640 --> 00:00:16,480
THE FOLLOWING TAKES PLACE BETWEEN SIX A.M. AND SEVEN A.M.

2
00:00:16,840 --> 00:00:19,040
AMERICA HAS BEEN VICTIMIZED AGAIN.

3
00:00:19,040 --> 00:00:23,400
LAST NIGHT'S TERRORIST ATTACK IN SAN ANTONIO IS NOW THE LATEST IN THIS SERIES OF BOMBINGS...

4
00:00:23,520 --> 00:00:26,280
THAT BEGAN ELEVEN WEEKS AGO IN TEN DIFFERENT CITIES.

5
00:00:26,280 --> 00:00:28,640
OVER NINE HUNDRED PEOPLE HAVE BEEN KILLED THUS FAR.

6
00:00:28,640 --> 00:00:31,960
AND WHILE NO ONE IS CLAIMING RESPONSIBILITY FOR THIS WAVE OF DEATH,

7
00:00:31,960 --> 00:00:34,520
EVIDENCE POINTS TO ISLAMIC MILITANTS.

8
00:00:34,520 --> 00:00:38,240
HERE IN LOS ANGELES, THE MOOD CAN ONLY BE DESCRIBED AS TENSE AND FEARFUL...

9
00:00:38,240 --> 00:00:40,960
AS THE DEPARTMENT OF HOMELAND SECURITY IS URGING ALL CITIZENS...

10
00:00:40,960 --> 00:00:45,000
TO REPORT, WITHOUT DELAY, ANY SUSPICIOUS PERSONS OR ACTIVITIES.

11
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:47,560
WE SPOKE WITH A DEPARTMENT SPOKESPERSON WHO SAYS, QUOTE,

12
00:00:47,560 --> 00:00:48,960
WE DON'T WANT TO START A WITCH HUNT,

13
00:00:49,080 --> 00:00:53,000
BUT WE WOULD RATHER ERR ON THE SIDE OF CAUTION THAN BECOME THE NEXT TARGET.

14
00:00:53,040 --> 00:00:55,520
HE THEN WENT ON TO SAY THAT THE VIGILANCE OF THE PUBLIC...

15
00:00:55,520 --> 00:00:59,280
IS OUR BEST LINE OF DEFENSE AGAINST ATTACK.

16
00:00:59,360 --> 00:01:01,640
HEY, HEY, HEY, HEY, HEY!

17
00:01:01,640 --> 00:01:05,200
HEY! STOP! STOP! STOP! OPEN THE DOORS!

18
00:01:05,200 --> 00:01:07,520
PLEASE. I HAVE TO GET TO WORK.

19
00:01:07,520 --> 00:01:12,680
I'LL BE LATE FOR WORK. PLEASE, OPEN THE DOOR.

20
00:01:12,760 --> 00:01:14,840
COME ON, MAN. OPEN THE DOOR.

21
00:01:15,960 --> 00:01:17,880
OPEN THE DOOR! I CAN'T BELIEVE YOU!

22
00:01:18,080 --> 00:01:21,200
I CAN'T BELIEVE YOU DIDN'T OPEN THE DOOR!

23
00:01:21,200 --> 00:01:23,040
I HAVE AS MUCH RIGHT TO BE ON THE BUS AS YOU!

24
00:02:00,800 --> 00:02:03,120
OUR COUNTRY IS UNDER SIEGE.

25
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:05,680
NOW, YOU'RE THE NATIONAL SECURITY ADVISER, KAREN.

26
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:07,840
FRANKLY, I'M SURPRISED BY YOUR RESISTANCE.

27
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:09,520
THESE PLACES THAT YOU KEEP BUILDING...

28
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:13,320
THEY'RE NOTHING MORE THAN CONCENTRATION CAMPS. DETENTION FACILITIES.

29
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:18,120
AND THE CRITERIA FOR DETERMINING WHO SHALL BE DETAINED ARE VERY REASONABLE.

30
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:20,640
REASONABLE? THIS REVISED PLAN OF YOURS...

31
00:02:20,720 --> 00:02:23,800
JUSTIFIES LOCKING UP EVERY AMERICAN WHO PRAYS TOWARDS MECCA.

32
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:25,720
THAT'S A RIDICULOUS EXAGGERATION, AND YOU KNOW IT.

33
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:28,880
RIGHT NOW, THE AMERICAN MUSLIM COMMUNITY IS OUR GREATEST ASSET.

34
00:02:28,880 --> 00:02:31,200
THEY HAVE PROVIDED LAW ENFORCEMENT WITH HUNDREDS OF TIPS,

35
00:02:31,200 --> 00:02:34,720
AND NOT A SINGLE MEMBER OF THAT COMMUNITY HAS BEEN IMPLICATED IN THESE ATTACKS.

36
00:02:34,880 --> 00:02:37,320
SO FAR. MISTER PRESIDENT,

37
00:02:37,320 --> 00:02:40,640
THE PEOPLE ARE LOSING FAITH IN OUR ABILITY TO PROTECT THEM.

38
00:02:40,640 --> 00:02:43,400
WE'VE GOT TO DO SOMETHING ABOUT THIS NOW.

39
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:46,440
AND LOCKING UP MORE MUSLIMS WILL NOT MAKE THEM SAFER.

40
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:49,240
NO, KAREN, BUT IT WILL MAKE THEM FEEL SAFER.

41
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:52,720
WHAT ABOUT THE COST OF THE CIVIL UNREST THAT YOUR PLAN WILL CREATE?

42
00:02:52,720 --> 00:02:56,920
THERE WILL BE RIOTS, DEMONSTRATIONS... SECURITY HAS ITS PRICE.

43
00:02:56,920 --> 00:02:59,760
SO DOES FREEDOM, TOM.

44
00:02:59,760 --> 00:03:02,720
LISTEN, I JUST DON'T SEE HOW I CAN SIGN OFF ON SOMETHING LIKE THIS.

45
00:03:02,720 --> 00:03:04,280
I MEAN, WASN'T IT JUST THREE MONTHS AGO...

46
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:07,800
THAT I TOOK AN OATH TO PRESERVE, PROTECT AND DEFEND THE CONSTITUTION?

47
00:03:07,880 --> 00:03:10,680
AND WHAT ABOUT PRESERVING, PROTECTING AND DEFENDING THE AMERICAN PEOPLE?

48
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:13,680
ALL OF THESE MEASURES ARE LEGAL.

49
00:03:13,720 --> 00:03:17,320
BLAKE HAS BEEN ALL OVER THIS THING WITH THE ATTORNEY GENERAL.

50
00:03:17,320 --> 00:03:19,640
THERE IS A PRECEDENT, SIR, ESPECIALLY IN WARTIME.

51
00:03:19,720 --> 00:03:22,480
LINCOLN SUSPENDED HABEAS CORPUS. ROOSEVELT SIGNED EXECUTIVE ORDER...

52
00:03:22,480 --> 00:03:27,280
YES, BLAKE, I KNOW THIS. AND ROOSEVELT IMPRISONED OVER 200,000 JAPANESE-AMERICANS...

53
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:30,160
IN WHAT MOST HISTORIANS CONSIDER TO BE A SHAMEFUL MISTAKE.

54
00:03:30,160 --> 00:03:33,720
WELL, I WOULD ASK THOSE HISTORIANS HOW MANY OF THOSE JAPANESE-AMERICANS...

55
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:38,520
WERE THUS PREVENTED FROM PERPETRATING ACTS OF SABOTAGE IN THIS COUNTRY.

56
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:41,560
I REALIZE THAT WHAT I'M PROPOSING HAS ITS CHALLENGES,

57
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:45,000
BUT WE CANNOT CONTINUE TO KEEP OUR HEADS BURIED IN THE SAND.

58
00:03:46,320 --> 00:03:48,040
MISTER PRESIDENT. YEAH?

59
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:52,280
- ANOTHER ATTACK? - LOS ANGELES. A BUS.

60
00:03:52,280 --> 00:04:00,560
- HOW MANY CASUALTIES? - TWENTY-THREE SO FAR, INCLUDING THE SUICIDE BOMBER.

61
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:12,240
AND WE'RE STILL CERTAIN THIS MAN ASSAD IS BEHIND ALL THESE ATTACKS, RIGHT?

62
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:14,760
YES, SIR. WE CONFIRMED HE ARRIVED IN THE UNITED STATES...

63
00:04:14,760 --> 00:04:17,400
THREE DAYS BEFORE THE FIRST BOMBING IN SAN ANTONIO.

64
00:04:17,400 --> 00:04:19,880
AND LET US NOT FORGET, ASSAD HAS BEEN CALLING...

65
00:04:19,880 --> 00:04:23,040
FOR THE DESTRUCTION OF THE UNITED STATES FOR THE LAST TWENTY YEARS.

66
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:26,080
MISTER PRESIDENT, MY ANALYSTS BELIEVE THAT ASSAD'S ORGANIZATION...

67
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:30,160
CANNOT SURVIVE WITHOUT HIM, AND ONCE HE'S DEAD, THESE ATTACKS WILL STOP.

68
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:34,760
SO THIS ASSUMES THE SUCCESS OF THE OPERATION TO TERMINATE ASSAD?

69
00:04:34,760 --> 00:04:37,880
C.T.U. ESTIMATES SUCCESSFUL PROBABILITY AT SEVENTY FIVE PERCENT.

70
00:04:37,880 --> 00:04:39,560
OH, I THINK THAT'S VERY GENEROUS.

71
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:42,440
YOU KNOW, IT... IT... IT SOUNDS TO ME LIKE YOU'RE ANTICIPATING FAILURE, TOM.

72
00:04:42,440 --> 00:04:46,160
I FULLY ACKNOWLEDGE, SIR, THAT THIS IS OUR ONLY OPTION,

73
00:04:46,160 --> 00:04:51,920
BUT I AM FERVENTLY ADVOCATING CONTINGENCIES.

74
00:04:52,320 --> 00:04:54,040
CONTINGENCIES ARE WELL AND GOOD, TOM.

75
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:59,200
BUT C.T.U. NEEDS TO ELIMINATE ASSAD. THAT'S ALL THERE IS TO IT.

76
00:05:00,840 --> 00:05:04,920
GOD KNOWS WE'RE PAYING A STEEP ENOUGH PRICE TO GET HIM.

77
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:08,640
I'VE TOLD YOU TWENTY TIMES, YOU DON'T SEND OUT A REPORT WITHOUT A CERTIFIED HEADER ON IT.

78
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:10,520
WELL, THIS MAKES TWENTY ONE. YOU SHOULD UPDATE YOUR COUNT.

79
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:13,000
DO YOU... AND I'M JUST CURIOUS...

80
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:16,000
EVER OPEN YOUR MOUTH WITHOUT SARCASM JUST SPILLING OUT OF IT?

81
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:19,160
SORRY, ARE WE DONE HERE? LOOK, I'M JUST TELLING YOU TO BE CAREFUL.

82
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:22,280
OTHERWISE YOU WILL FIND YOURSELF BACK SELLING LADIES SHOES IN BEVERLY HILLS.

83
00:05:22,280 --> 00:05:24,840
YOU'RE REALLY SETTLING WELL INTO THE WHOLE MIDDLE-MANAGEMENT THING, AREN'T YOU?

84
00:05:24,840 --> 00:05:27,320
WHAT'S YOUR PROBLEM WITH ME? I LIKED YOU FINE AS AN ANALYST.

85
00:05:27,320 --> 00:05:31,480
ACTUALLY YOU WERE VERY GOOD. AS A BOSS, BIT OF A BORE.

86
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:33,800
RIGHT.

87
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:36,040
WHAT'S GOING ON?

88
00:05:36,440 --> 00:05:41,800
TALK TO YOUR BOYFRIEND. THE GUY'S ON SELF-DESTRUCT.

89
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,880
YOU PROMISED ME YOU'D GET ALONG WITH MILO.

90
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:48,680
I'M SORRY, DARLING. THAT'S A PROMISE I JUST CAN'T KEEP.

91
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:53,360
MORRIS. MORRIS.

92
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:55,080
YOU KNOW, I HAD THE SAME PROBLEM WITH DEPARTMENT HEADS...

93
00:05:55,080 --> 00:05:56,840
WHEN I FIRST STARTED, AND I LEARNED HOW TO FIT IN.

94
00:05:56,960 --> 00:06:01,360
THERE'S NO REASON WHY YOU CAN'T. EXCEPT I DON'T HAPPEN TO BE A PRETTY LADY.

95
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:04,440
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT? YOU'RE A HOTTIE.

96
00:06:04,640 --> 00:06:07,800
NO, I'M NOT. YES, YOU ARE. DEAL WITH IT.

97
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:08,800
MORRIS, WE'RE AT WORK. SO?

98
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:12,200
IT'S UNPROFESSIONAL. ARE YOU SAYING YOU DON'T LIKE IT?

99
00:06:12,280 --> 00:06:16,080
NO, I'M NOT SAYING THAT. I JUST CAME TO SEE IF YOU GOT A REQUEST FROM HOMELAND...

100
00:06:16,080 --> 00:06:17,800
ON THE PRIORITY CHANNEL. NO.

101
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:20,640
WELL, WHY DID THEY SEND IT ONLY TO ME?

102
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:25,720
I DON'T KNOW. JUST TRY TO GET ALONG.

103
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:31,080
BECAUSE YOU ASKED, I WILL.

104
00:06:31,520 --> 00:06:34,560
NADIA, I JUST GOT A WEIRD REQUEST FROM HOMELAND SECURITY.

105
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:37,280
THEY WANT TO SET UP A CHANNEL, AND I WANTED TO CLEAR WITH YOU FIRST.

106
00:06:37,280 --> 00:06:41,320
- CONSIDER YOURSELF CLEARED. - THEY WANT IT FORMATTED ACCORDING TO MILITARY SPECS.

107
00:06:41,320 --> 00:06:44,080
COORDINATING AN ASSAULT WITH THE COBRA ATTACK HELICOPTERS FROM CAMP PENDLETON.

108
00:06:44,200 --> 00:06:46,560
WHEN? THIRTY MINUTES.

109
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:49,200
- AN ASSAULT ON WHO? - ASSAD.

110
00:06:50,080 --> 00:06:52,200
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT? WE DON'T EVEN KNOW WHERE ASSAD IS.

111
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:56,040
WE WILL. WE HAVE A LEAD. NO, WE DON'T. IF WE DID, I WOULD KNOW ABOUT IT.

112
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:58,600
WE FOUND A WAY TO GET ASSAD'S LOCATION.

113
00:06:58,880 --> 00:07:02,440
HOW?

114
00:07:03,440 --> 00:07:07,360
JACK BAUER. JACK'S IN A CHINESE PRISON.

115
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:09,720
NOT ANYMORE. THE PRESIDENT NEGOTIATED HIS RELEASE TWO DAYS AGO.

116
00:07:11,960 --> 00:07:15,800
JACK'S COMING BACK? YES.

117
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:18,080
WELL, WHY DID THE CHINESE LET HIM GO? WHY TODAY?

118
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:19,600
DOES THIS HAVE SOMETHING TO DO WITH THE ATTACKS?

119
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:21,360
HOW DO WE THINK JACK'S GONNA LEAD US TO ASSAD?

120
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:26,200
CHLOE, I CAN'T TALK ABOUT THIS. NOT YET. WHY NOT?

121
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:30,320
CAN BILL BUCHANAN TALK ABOUT IT? HE'S MEETING JACK AT POINT MUGU NAVAL AIR STATION.

122
00:07:30,320 --> 00:07:48,320
NOW OPEN THAT MILITARY CHANNEL PUT IT THROUGH TO THE CONFERENCE AREA.

123
00:07:48,400 --> 00:07:50,760
THE PRESIDENT MUST HAVE GIVEN UP A LOT TO MAKE THIS HAPPEN.

124
00:07:52,080 --> 00:07:56,760
I WISH HE WERE COMING BACK UNDER DIFFERENT CIRCUMSTANCES.

125
00:07:57,160 --> 00:07:59,680
WE DON'T KNOW WHAT HIS STATE OF MIND WILL BE.

126
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:37,160
IF HE DOESN'T COOPERATE, WE NEED TO BE PREPARED.

127
00:08:37,640 --> 00:08:41,520
MISTER BUCHANAN, I NEED YOUR SIGNATURE ON THIS RELEASE DOCUMENT.

128
00:08:41,560 --> 00:08:44,720
TAKE THOSE CUFFS OFF HIM.

129
00:08:56,720 --> 00:09:16,560
JACK. IT'S OKAY. COME WITH ME.

130
00:09:16,640 --> 00:09:21,400
PLEASE CONVEY TO YOUR PRESIDENT THAT MISTER BAUER NEVER BROKE HIS SILENCE.

131
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:25,880
HE HASN'T SPOKEN A WORD IN NEARLY TWO YEARS.

132
00:09:25,960 --> 00:09:29,880
YOUR PRESIDENT HAS PAID A HIGH PRICE FOR MISTER BAUER'S FREEDOM.

133
00:09:29,880 --> 00:09:45,280
WHAT HE WANTS FROM HIM MUST BE VERY IMPORTANT.

134
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:54,360
PRESIDENT PALMER WANTS TO SPEAK TO YOU HIMSELF AS SOON AS WE DEBRIEF.

135
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:56,960
I'M SORRY, JACK. HOW COULD YOU KNOW?

136
00:09:56,960 --> 00:09:59,240
WAYNE PALMER IS PRESIDENT.

137
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:00,920
HE'S THE ONE WHO NEGOTIATED YOUR RELEASE.

138
00:10:02,280 --> 00:10:05,000
I CAN'T EVEN BEGIN TO IMAGINE WHAT YOU WENT THROUGH OVER, JACK.

139
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:11,040
BUT THERE'S A REASON YOU'RE HERE NOW.

140
00:10:11,600 --> 00:10:16,960
THE LAST ELEVEB WEEKS, OUR CITIES HAVE BEEN TARGETED BY A SERIES OF TERROR ATTACKS.

141
00:10:17,040 --> 00:10:19,840
BUSES, TRAINS, SHOPPING MALLS.

142
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:24,680
THE LAST ONE WAS FIFTEEN MINUTES AGO HERE IN LOS ANGELES.

143
00:10:24,680 --> 00:10:25,960
IT'S HAMRI AL-ASSAD.

144
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:29,280
ASSAD'S HERE, JACK.

145
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:35,600
FOUR DAYS AGO, ONE OF ASSAD'S MEN CONTACTED US.

146
00:10:35,640 --> 00:10:39,480
HE SAID HE'D GIVE UP ASSAD FOR TWENTY FIVE MILLION DOLLARS.

147
00:10:39,480 --> 00:10:43,520
BUT HE'S DEMANDING SOMETHING MORE THAN MONEY.

148
00:10:43,520 --> 00:10:47,760
HE WANTS YOU, JACK.

149
00:10:47,760 --> 00:10:52,520
HE WANTS YOU DEAD.

150
00:10:56,040 --> 00:10:59,040
IT'S ABU FAYED.

151
00:10:59,040 --> 00:11:01,240
HE WANTS HIS POUND OF FLESH FOR WHAT HAPPENED IN BEIRUT.

152
00:11:03,160 --> 00:11:06,400
WE OFFERED HIM OTHER ALTERNATIVES. WE DID EVERYTHING WE COULD THINK OF, JACK.

153
00:11:08,520 --> 00:11:11,560
BUT HE WOULD ONLY AGREE TO GIVE US ASSAD IN EXCHANGE FOR YOU.

154
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:15,880
HE'S DEMANDED OUR SURVEILLANCE PROTOCOLS,

155
00:11:15,880 --> 00:11:18,880
WHICH MEANS WE CAN'T RISK AN EXTRACTION.

156
00:11:18,880 --> 00:11:23,080
ONCE HE HAS YOU, YOU'LL BE ON YOUR OWN.

157
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:24,520
YOU UNDERSTAND WHAT THIS MEANS, JACK?

158
00:11:25,720 --> 00:11:28,880
WE'RE ASKING YOU TO SACRIFICE YOURSELF,

159
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:33,840
SO WE CAN ELIMINATE ASSAD.

160
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:39,320
I CAN'T HEAR YOU, JACK.

161
00:11:42,320 --> 00:11:42,720
AUDREY?

162
00:11:44,120 --> 00:11:45,480
AUDREY DOESN'T KNOW YOU'RE BACK.

163
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:47,880
MY DAUGHTER?

164
00:11:49,280 --> 00:11:50,400
KIM DOESN'T KNOW EITHER.

165
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:59,520
YOU KEEP IT THAT WAY.

166
00:12:01,520 --> 00:12:03,520
I KNOW WHAT'S BEING ASKED OF ME, CURTIS.

167
00:12:03,680 --> 00:12:08,840
YOU DON'T NEED YOUR FIREARM.

168
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:12,240
BEFORE WE DO THIS,

169
00:12:12,280 --> 00:12:15,080
I WOULD LIKE TO CLEAN UP.

170
00:12:15,160 --> 00:12:16,560
WE'VE GOT AN AREA SET UP FOR YOU,

171
00:12:16,880 --> 00:12:58,960
AND BROUGHT YOU SOME NEW CLOTHES.

172
00:12:59,240 --> 00:13:08,680
BILL?

173
00:13:09,600 --> 00:13:13,040
WE HAVE JACK. GOOD.

174
00:13:13,040 --> 00:13:18,440
I THOUGHT I WAS PREPARED, BUT HE'S WORSE THAN I EXPECTED. MUCH WORSE.

175
00:13:18,720 --> 00:13:20,760
I KNOW HOW HARD THIS MUST BE FOR YOU,

176
00:13:21,200 --> 00:13:24,600
BUT EVERYTHING DEPENDS ON THIS OPERATION.

177
00:13:24,600 --> 00:13:25,320
I UNDERSTAND.

178
00:13:26,840 --> 00:13:28,240
I KNOW YOU DO.

179
00:13:32,520 --> 00:13:35,280
I WISH I WERE THERE WITH YOU.

180
00:13:35,400 --> 00:13:36,480
YOU'RE WHERE YOU NEED TO BE.

181
00:13:38,440 --> 00:13:40,680
I MISS YOU.

182
00:13:40,680 --> 00:13:43,560
I MISS YOU TOO.

183
00:13:43,560 --> 00:13:46,080
I HAVE TO TAKE JACK TO THE DROP POINT NOW.

184
00:13:46,080 --> 00:13:48,560
BYE.

185
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:53,800
LOS ANGELES HAS NOW BEEN ADDED TO THE LIST OF MAJOR CITIES HIT BY TERRORIST ATTACKS.

186
00:13:53,800 --> 00:13:57,400
THE DEPARTMENT OF HOMELAND SECURITY HAS RAISED THE THREAT LEVEL TO RED...

187
00:13:57,560 --> 00:13:59,840
THE HIGHEST LEVEL SINCE THE DEPARTMENT WAS FORMED.

188
00:13:59,840 --> 00:14:02,200
F.B.I. WILL HANDLE ALL THE FIELD SEARCHES OUTSIDE THE CITY,

189
00:14:02,200 --> 00:14:03,720
SO JUST FOCUS ON THE MAIN GRID. YES, MA'AM.

190
00:14:03,720 --> 00:14:06,200
NADIA, I NEED TO TALK TO YOU.

191
00:14:06,200 --> 00:14:08,160
RIGHT. FINISH THAT UP AND CHECK BACK WITH ME. OKAY.

192
00:14:08,160 --> 00:14:10,480
DID YOU OPEN THAT MILITARY CHANNEL PUT IT THROUGH TO THE CONFERENCE AREA?

193
00:14:10,480 --> 00:14:13,560
YEAH. I'VE BEEN TRYING TO LOCATE BILL OR CURTIS TO FIND OUT WHAT'S GOING ON WITH JACK,

194
00:14:13,560 --> 00:14:15,760
BUT THEY'RE BOTH OFF-LINE, AND THERE'S A BLOCK ON THEIR STATUS ROSTERS.

195
00:14:15,760 --> 00:14:18,120
I TOLD YOU, CHLOE. I CAN'T TALK ABOUT THIS.

196
00:14:18,120 --> 00:14:21,320
NADIA, YOU'VE ONLY BEEN HERE A COUPLE MONTHS, SO YOU DON'T KNOW ME VERY WELL,

197
00:14:21,320 --> 00:14:24,400
BUT IF YOU DID, YOU WOULD KNOW HOW MUCH JACK BAUER MEANS TO ME.

198
00:14:24,480 --> 00:14:28,360
YOU WOULD ALSO KNOW THAT SOONER OR LATER I WILL FIND OUT. SO WHY DON'T YOU JUST TELL ME RIGHT NOW?

199
00:14:28,360 --> 00:14:29,440
CHLOE, I DON'T HAVE THE AUTHORIZATION...

200
00:14:29,440 --> 00:14:31,520
OKAY, WHY DON'T I JUST CALL DIVISION AND LET THEM KNOW...

201
00:14:31,520 --> 00:14:35,760
ABOUT THE TIME THAT YOU LEFT THE JARVIS FIREWALL UNSECURED?

202
00:14:35,760 --> 00:14:42,920
IF IT WEREN'T FOR ME, YOU WOULD HAVE BEEN FIRED OVER THAT.

203
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:46,120
WE WERE CONTACTED FOUR DAYS AGO BY A MAN NAMED FAYED.

204
00:14:46,920 --> 00:14:51,120
HE OFFERED TO GIVE US ASSAD'S LOCATION FOR A LIST OF DEMANDS. ONE OF THEM WAS JACK BAUER.

205
00:14:52,600 --> 00:14:54,040
JACK? WHY DOES HE WANT JACK?

206
00:14:54,680 --> 00:14:57,920
RETRIBUTION. RETRIBUTION FOR WHAT?

207
00:14:57,920 --> 00:15:01,520
FAYED'S BROTHER WAS PART OF THE CELL THAT BOMBED OUR EMBASSY IN LEBANON IN NINETEEN NINETY NINE.

208
00:15:01,520 --> 00:15:04,320
JACK WAS SENT IN TO GRAB HIM AND GET THE NAMES OF THE OTHER CELL MEMBERS.

209
00:15:04,320 --> 00:15:07,440
FAYED'S BROTHER DIED WHILE JACK WAS INTERROGATING HIM.

210
00:15:07,440 --> 00:15:10,000
NOW HE WANTS JACK DEAD. THAT'S RIGHT.

211
00:15:11,160 --> 00:15:16,280
AND YOU'RE REALLY GONNA JUST DELIVER JACK OVER TO THE TERRORISTS TO BE KILLED?

212
00:15:16,280 --> 00:15:17,800
- NADIA... - WE NEED TO STOP ASSAD.

213
00:15:17,840 --> 00:15:21,560
WHY AREN'T WE ORGANIZING A RESCUE? WE CAN GRAB JACK ONCE FAYED GIVES US ASSAD'S LOCATION.

214
00:15:21,560 --> 00:15:24,240
FAYED HAS THE RESOURCES TO DETECT OUR SURVEILLANCE.

215
00:15:24,240 --> 00:15:27,920
AS PART OF THE DEAL, WE GAVE FAYED MONITORING ACCESS TO OUR SATELLITE COVERAGE,

216
00:15:27,920 --> 00:15:29,520
RADIO FREQUENCIES AND AIR CORRIDORS.

217
00:15:30,120 --> 00:15:32,680
HE WON'T GIVE US ANYTHING UNTIL HE'S FREE AND CLEAR WITH JACK.

218
00:15:32,960 --> 00:15:34,720
HOW DO WE EVEN KNOW HE'LL DO WHAT HE SAYS?

219
00:15:35,360 --> 00:15:39,440
WE DON'T.

220
00:15:39,800 --> 00:15:42,400
I'M CALLING KAREN HAYES. SHE'LL TALK TO THE PRESIDENT.

221
00:15:42,400 --> 00:15:45,440
CHLOE, DON'T YOU GET IT? KAREN ALREADY KNOWS.

222
00:15:45,440 --> 00:15:51,240
SO DOES PRESIDENT PALMER. HE AUTHORIZED IT.

223
00:15:53,200 --> 00:15:57,360
LOOK,

224
00:15:59,080 --> 00:16:01,240
I'M SORRY ABOUT YOUR FRIEND,

225
00:16:01,240 --> 00:16:04,000
BUT THERE'S NOTHING YOU, I OR ANYONE CAN DO.

226
00:16:04,040 --> 00:16:07,200
RIGHT NOW, THIS IS OUR ONLY WAY OUT OF THIS CRISIS.

227
00:16:07,200 --> 00:16:51,520
IF WE WANT THESE ATTACKS TO STOP, JACK BAUER HAS TO BE SACRIFICED.

228
00:16:52,360 --> 00:16:55,760
I'VE ONLY GOTTEN HALF THOSE UPGRADES. YOU'LL GET THE REST IN A MINUTE.

229
00:16:55,960 --> 00:16:59,040
NO, I NEED THEM NOW, MORRIS. I NEEDED THEM 10 MINUTES AGO.

230
00:16:59,040 --> 00:17:01,440
AND DON'T EXPECT CHLOE TO KEEP RUNNING INTERFERENCE FOR YOU.

231
00:17:01,440 --> 00:17:03,520
YOU'LL GET YOUR UPGRADES. WHEN?

232
00:17:09,160 --> 00:17:10,560
WHAT'S GOING ON BETWEEN YOU AND NADIA?

233
00:17:12,200 --> 00:17:14,160
THE PRESIDENT GOT JACK BACK FROM THE CHINESE.

234
00:17:14,400 --> 00:17:18,280
HE'S IN L.A. NOW. WELL, THAT'S VERY GOOD NEWS.

235
00:17:18,280 --> 00:17:29,080
NO, MORRIS, IT'S NOT.

236
00:17:29,080 --> 00:17:30,960
BUCHANAN. BILL, IT'S THE PRESIDENT. IS JACK WITH YOU?

237
00:17:31,120 --> 00:17:32,840
YES, SIR. WE'RE ALMOST TO THE DROP POINT.

238
00:17:32,840 --> 00:17:34,840
LET ME SPEAK TO HIM, PLEASE.

239
00:17:34,840 --> 00:17:36,560
I'LL PUT HIM ON. JACK.

240
00:17:38,680 --> 00:17:42,560
JACK.

241
00:17:43,000 --> 00:17:51,920
IT'S PRESIDENT PALMER. HE WANTS TO TALK TO YOU.

242
00:17:51,920 --> 00:17:54,120
MISTER PRESIDENT. JACK.

243
00:17:54,760 --> 00:17:58,480
I'VE BEEN TRYING TO THINK OF WHAT I COULD POSSIBLY SAY TO YOU,

244
00:17:58,480 --> 00:18:01,240
AFTER ALL THAT YOU'VE SACRIFICED FOR THIS COUNTRY,

245
00:18:01,240 --> 00:18:02,560
WHAT YOU'VE DONE FOR ME IN THE PAST,

246
00:18:02,560 --> 00:18:05,600
AND, OF COURSE, WHAT YOU'VE DONE FOR MY BROTHER DAVID.

247
00:18:06,560 --> 00:18:08,840
THIS IS A DESPERATE MEASURE, JACK. BELIEVE ME, I KNOW.

248
00:18:08,840 --> 00:18:10,800
BUT IT'S ALSO A MEASURE OF OUR DESPERATION.

249
00:18:11,840 --> 00:18:14,280
PEOPLE ARE AFRAID TO COME OUTSIDE.

250
00:18:14,280 --> 00:18:15,840
THEY'RE AFRAID TO LEAVE THEIR HOMES, JACK.

251
00:18:15,840 --> 00:18:18,080
I MEAN, THEY'RE ACTUALLY STARTING TO TURN AGAINST EACH OTHER OUT THERE.

252
00:18:18,120 --> 00:18:23,560
BILL BUCHANAN EXPLAINED THE SITUATION, SIR. I KNOW WHAT'S HAPPENING.

253
00:18:23,640 --> 00:18:26,800
I UNDERSTAND WHAT'S EXPECTED OF ME.

254
00:18:29,560 --> 00:18:31,640
YOU HAVE MY WORD... MY WORD, JACK...

255
00:18:31,640 --> 00:18:34,880
YOUR SACRIFICE WILL NOT BE IN VAIN.

256
00:18:35,080 --> 00:18:35,600
THANK YOU.

257
00:18:37,280 --> 00:18:46,600
GOD BLESS YOU, JACK. GOOD-BYE, MISTER PRESIDENT.

258
00:18:47,080 --> 00:18:52,160
WHEN I AGREED TO RUN FOR THIS OFFICE, I THOUGHT THAT I UNDERSTOOD THIS JOB.

259
00:18:52,160 --> 00:18:53,920
I MEAN, I WAS RIGHT BESIDE MY BROTHER DAVID...

260
00:18:53,920 --> 00:18:56,600
WHEN HE HAD TO MAKE IMPOSSIBLE DECISIONS, YOU KNOW?

261
00:18:56,680 --> 00:18:59,240
TIMES WHEN HE HAD TO CHOOSE BETWEEN BAD OPTIONS.

262
00:18:59,280 --> 00:19:02,880
BUT NOW THAT I'M THE ONE SITTING IN THAT CHAIR,

263
00:19:02,880 --> 00:19:07,400
I'M STARTING TO WONDER IF I'M THE RIGHT PERSON TO LEAD THIS COUNTRY.

264
00:19:07,640 --> 00:19:09,240
IT'S AN IRRELEVANT QUESTION, SIR.

265
00:19:09,840 --> 00:19:10,440
EXCUSE ME?

266
00:19:11,880 --> 00:19:13,960
YOU WILL LEAD THIS COUNTRY,

267
00:19:13,960 --> 00:19:15,360
WHETHER YOU WANT TO OR NOT.

268
00:19:17,360 --> 00:19:22,280
YOU ARE THE PRESIDENT.

269
00:19:22,280 --> 00:19:25,640
WELL, THIS PRESIDENT CAN'T SHAKE THE FEELING...

270
00:19:25,680 --> 00:19:27,880
THAT SACRIFICING JACK BAUER IS A MISTAKE,

271
00:19:27,880 --> 00:19:31,000
AND THAT MAYBE I SHOULD CALL THIS WHOLE THING OFF BEFORE IT'S TOO LATE.

272
00:19:31,000 --> 00:19:35,360
NO, SIR. YOU HAVE NOT MADE A MISTAKE.

273
00:19:35,440 --> 00:19:38,480
AND, FOR WHAT IT'S WORTH, YOUR BROTHER...

274
00:19:38,720 --> 00:19:41,400
WOULD BE DOING JUST THE SAME THING.

275
00:19:41,400 --> 00:19:42,480
THAT DOESN'T MAKE IT RIGHT.

276
00:19:42,920 --> 00:19:45,360
IT ISN'T RIGHT. IT ISN'T WRONG.

277
00:19:45,960 --> 00:19:49,120
IT'S SIMPLY OUR ONLY OPTION.

278
00:19:49,160 --> 00:20:05,080
BAUER HAS TO BE SACRIFICED SO THIS COUNTRY CAN SURVIVE.

279
00:20:05,200 --> 00:20:08,880
- I JUST HEARD A DISTURBING RUMOR. - WHAT RUMOR'S THAT?

280
00:20:09,200 --> 00:20:12,320
THAT YOU'RE AUTHORIZING THE NATIONAL GUARD TO SET UP DETENTION FACILITIES...

281
00:20:12,320 --> 00:20:16,480
AT CONVENTION CENTERS AND SPORTS ARENAS IN LOS ANGELES, DETROIT AND PHILADELPHIA.

282
00:20:16,480 --> 00:20:18,560
YEAH, THAT... THAT'S CORRECT.

283
00:20:18,680 --> 00:20:22,120
THAT'S AGAINST THE PRESIDENT'S ORDER. I WAS THERE WHEN HE GAVE IT.

284
00:20:22,120 --> 00:20:24,840
KAREN, I KNOW WHERE YOU WERE. I WAS STANDING RIGHT NEXT TO YOU.

285
00:20:26,280 --> 00:20:28,520
TO MY KNOWLEDGE, THAT ORDER HASN'T BEEN RESCINDED.

286
00:20:29,920 --> 00:20:32,080
ALL RIGHT, YOU WERE CONFUSED.

287
00:20:32,080 --> 00:20:35,480
I HAVEN'T IMPLEMENTED ANYTHING YET. I'M MERELY POSITIONING.

288
00:20:35,600 --> 00:20:37,760
IF THE PRESIDENT CHANGES HIS MIND,

289
00:20:37,760 --> 00:20:41,760
AS I SUSPECT HE WILL, THEN WE WILL HAVE WASTED LESS TIME.

290
00:20:41,760 --> 00:20:44,920
I'M NOT CONFUSED, TOM. AND YOU CAN USE WHATEVER WORDS YOU LIKE.

291
00:20:45,000 --> 00:20:48,200
IN PLAIN ENGLISH, YOU'RE SECOND-GUESSING THE PRESIDENT.

292
00:20:48,520 --> 00:20:52,320
PLAIN ENGLISH DOES NOT ALLOW FOR THE NUANCES THAT MY JOB REQUIRES, KAREN.

293
00:20:52,320 --> 00:20:53,720
AND JUST HOW FAR ARE YOU GONNA PUSH THIS?

294
00:20:54,040 --> 00:20:56,040
THE ACLU IS ALREADY FILING COMPLAINTS...

295
00:20:56,040 --> 00:20:58,480
AGAINST US THAT WE'VE GIVEN THE BUREAU TOO MUCH FIELD AUTHORITY.

296
00:20:58,560 --> 00:21:01,240
AND, BY MY LIGHTS, THEY HAVE NOT BEEN GIVEN NEAR ENOUGH.

297
00:21:01,240 --> 00:21:03,200
THEY NEED A WIDER NET WITH TIGHTER MESH.

298
00:21:03,200 --> 00:21:05,800
AND WHAT HAPPENS WHEN INNOCENT PEOPLE GET CAUGHT IN THAT NET?

299
00:21:05,880 --> 00:21:08,800
WELL, LIKE I TOLD YOU BEFORE, SECURITY HAS ITS PRICE.

300
00:21:08,800 --> 00:21:10,760
JUST GET USED TO IT, KAREN.

301
00:21:23,600 --> 00:21:24,600
GO AHEAD.

302
00:21:24,600 --> 00:21:28,280
SECURE BAUER'S WRIST TO THE GRATE. THEN LEAVE HIM THERE.

303
00:21:28,280 --> 00:21:29,600
FIRST TELL ME WHERE ASSAD IS.

304
00:21:29,680 --> 00:21:31,680
THIS ISN'T A NEGOTIATION.

305
00:21:31,680 --> 00:21:34,400
IF YOU WANT ASSAD, LEAVE BAUER HERE,

306
00:21:34,400 --> 00:21:36,600
GET BACK IN YOUR CAR AND DRIVE AWAY.

307
00:21:36,760 --> 00:21:37,720
I'M WATCHING YOU.

308
00:21:40,320 --> 00:21:46,040
YOU LISTEN TO ME, YOU SON OF A BITCH.

309
00:21:46,400 --> 00:21:51,480
HE WANTS ME TO HANDCUFF YOU TO THAT GRATE.

310
00:21:52,040 --> 00:22:07,520
DO IT.

311
00:22:07,720 --> 00:22:12,840
I DON'T KNOW WHAT TO SAY, JACK.

312
00:22:12,960 --> 00:22:19,440
DO YOU UNDERSTAND THE DIFFERENCE BETWEEN DYING FOR SOMETHING AND DYING FOR NOTHING?

313
00:22:19,440 --> 00:22:22,160
THE ONLY REASON I FOUGHT SO HARD TO STAY ALIVE IN CHINA...

314
00:22:22,200 --> 00:22:26,600
WAS BECAUSE I DIDN'T WANT TO DIE FOR NOTHING.

315
00:22:27,760 --> 00:22:29,120
AND TODAY...

316
00:22:31,000 --> 00:22:34,320
I CAN DIE FOR SOMETHING.

317
00:22:34,440 --> 00:22:43,560
MY WAY, MY CHOICE.

318
00:22:43,560 --> 00:22:52,680
TO BE HONEST WITH YOU, IT'LL BE A RELIEF.

319
00:22:52,760 --> 00:22:54,960
I'M SORRY, JACK. DON'T BE.

320
00:22:57,320 --> 00:23:25,320
BILL, YOU NEED TO GO.

321
00:23:28,480 --> 00:23:29,200
GO.

322
00:23:34,000 --> 00:23:37,960
FIREMEN ARE BATTLING A FIRE AT THE AL-HAMZA MOSQUE IN CULVER CITY.

323
00:23:37,960 --> 00:23:40,000
MEMBERS OF THE MOSQUE ARE CALLING THE INCIDENT...

324
00:23:40,000 --> 00:23:42,880
A RETALIATION FOR THIS MORNING'S SUICIDE BOMBING...

325
00:23:42,880 --> 00:23:45,000
THAT HAPPENED DOWNTOWN ON A METRO BUS.

326
00:23:45,000 --> 00:23:48,120
SCOTT SHOULDN'T BE GOIN' TO SCHOOL. HE HAS A GEOMETRY TEST.

327
00:23:48,200 --> 00:23:53,640
HONEY, L.A. WAS JUST HIT. I MEAN, THEY SHOULD BE CLOSING THESE SCHOOLS DOWN.

328
00:23:55,120 --> 00:23:57,360
THEY WILL CLOSE THEM DOWN WHEN IT'S NOT SAFE.

329
00:23:57,360 --> 00:23:59,880
BUT UNTIL THEN, I DON'T WANNA SCARE OUR SON,

330
00:24:00,040 --> 00:24:02,240
AND I DON'T WANT YOU SCARING HIM EITHER.

331
00:24:02,240 --> 00:24:05,080
I WANT US TO KEEP LIVING OUR LIVES AS NORMALLY AS WE CAN.

332
00:24:05,280 --> 00:24:08,920
LOOK, JILLIAN, THERE IS NOTHING NORMAL, WHAT'S HAPPENING HERE.

333
00:24:08,920 --> 00:24:09,800
WELL, WHAT ARE WE SUPPOSED TO DO?

334
00:24:09,800 --> 00:24:12,480
- JUST HIDE INSIDE OUR HOUSE FOR THE REST OF OUR LIVES? - NO, IT'S SHOU...

335
00:24:13,960 --> 00:24:16,120
HEY. WAS AHMED ABLE TO HELP?

336
00:24:16,120 --> 00:24:18,440
I DIDN'T GET A CHANCE TO SEE HIM. THE F.B.I. ARE AT HIS HOUSE.

337
00:24:18,440 --> 00:24:20,880
THEY'RE ARRESTING HIS DAD. WHAT?

338
00:24:20,880 --> 00:24:31,600
- WHY ARE THEY TAKING HIM? - I DON'T KNOW.

339
00:24:31,920 --> 00:24:34,440
THIS IS INSANE! YOU CAN'T ARREST SOMEBODY WITHOUT A REASON.

340
00:24:35,240 --> 00:24:38,880
HE'S NOT A TERRORIST!

341
00:24:39,280 --> 00:24:41,800
HE'S INNOCENT!

342
00:24:41,800 --> 00:24:57,320
THERE'S GOTTA BE SOME REASON. I'M SURE IT'S A MISTAKE.

343
00:24:58,280 --> 00:25:00,840
AHMED! WHAT ARE YOU DOIN'?

344
00:25:01,040 --> 00:25:03,080
WE JUST WANNA TALK TO YOU, OKAY?

345
00:25:03,760 --> 00:25:05,320
AHMED, GET OUT HERE!

346
00:25:05,440 --> 00:25:08,360
IT'S THAT GUY DOWN THE BLOCK. THAT CONTRACTOR... STAN SOMETHING.

347
00:25:08,400 --> 00:25:11,680
YEAH, I KNOW. I'LL CALL THE POLICE. COME ON!

348
00:25:11,680 --> 00:25:14,960
WHY DON'T YOU GET THE HELL OUT OF MY NEIGHBORHOOD!

349
00:25:15,240 --> 00:25:17,200
WHAT ARE YOU DOING? I'M HELPING AHMED.

350
00:25:17,520 --> 00:25:19,040
YOUR FATHER IS CALLING THE POLICE.

351
00:25:19,040 --> 00:25:22,160
- THEY WON'T DO ANYTHING. - SCOTT, STOP. YOU'RE NOT GOING OVER THERE.

352
00:25:22,240 --> 00:25:24,800
DAD, I'M NOT HIDING HERE WHILE AHMED GETS BEAT UP,

353
00:25:24,800 --> 00:25:31,120
- 'CAUSE YOU'RE SCARED TO DO THE RIGHT THING. - SCOTT, STAY HERE.

354
00:25:33,840 --> 00:25:38,160
I'LL HANDLE IT.

355
00:25:39,240 --> 00:25:51,120
HEY, HEY, HEY, HEY. I I JUST WANNA TALK TO YOU.

356
00:25:51,120 --> 00:25:54,760
- GET OUT OF MY HOUSE. - WE'RE JUST HERE TO GIVE YOU A LITTLE FRIENDLY ADVICE, OKAY?

357
00:25:54,760 --> 00:25:56,560
STAN! STAN! WHAT THE HELL ARE YOU DOIN', MAN?

358
00:25:56,560 --> 00:25:59,160
I'M TRYIN' TO PROTECT MY FAMILY, RAY.

359
00:25:59,280 --> 00:26:00,800
THIS KID'S FATHER'S A TERRORIST.

360
00:26:00,800 --> 00:26:04,040
OH, COME ON. HE'S NO MORE OF A TERRORIST THAN YOU OR ME. YEAH?

361
00:26:04,040 --> 00:26:07,920
THEN WHY'D THEY ARREST HIM? BECAUSE THEY'RE SCARED, LIKE EVERYONE ELSE.

362
00:26:07,920 --> 00:26:10,800
AW, GET OUT OF MY WAY. HEY, STAN, COME ON! STAN.

363
00:26:12,080 --> 00:26:20,160
WHAT? IF YOU WANT HIM, YOU'RE COMING THROUGH ME.

364
00:26:23,760 --> 00:26:32,520
THIS ISN'T OVER, RAY.

365
00:26:35,320 --> 00:26:37,040
YOU ALL RIGHT? YEAH.

366
00:26:37,040 --> 00:26:41,040
ALL RIGHT, LOOK, UM, I... I THINK WHAT WE SHOULD DO IS, YOU SHOULD COME STAY WITH US...

367
00:26:41,080 --> 00:26:42,720
UNTIL THINGS GET SORTED OUT WITH YOUR FATHER.

368
00:26:42,760 --> 00:26:45,760
LOOK, I APPRECIATE WHAT YOU JUST DID, BUT I'LL BE FINE.

369
00:26:45,800 --> 00:26:50,440
LOOK, THIS GUY... THIS GUY IS A JERK. I DON'T WANT YOU STAYING HERE ALONE. IT'S DANGEROUS.

370
00:26:50,440 --> 00:26:53,600
I'M NOT TAKING NO FOR AN ANSWER. YOU'RE COMING WITH ME.

371
00:26:53,600 --> 00:26:55,600
NADIA. BILL BUCHANAN FOR YOU. RIGHT.

372
00:26:57,000 --> 00:26:59,800
- BILL. - JACK'S AT THE DROP POINT. ARE WE SET WITH THE MILITARY?

373
00:26:59,800 --> 00:27:02,360
THE MARINES HAVE TWO COBRA ATTACK HELICOPTERS READY TO DEPLOY.

374
00:27:02,360 --> 00:27:04,600
WE CAN HIT ANY TARGET INSIDE L.A. WITHIN TWENTY MINUTES.

375
00:27:04,640 --> 00:27:06,400
JACK'S GIVING HIS LIFE FOR THIS OPERATION,

376
00:27:06,720 --> 00:27:08,720
SO I DON'T WANT ANY MISTAKES.

377
00:27:08,720 --> 00:27:11,080
ASSAD MUST BE TAKEN OUT WITH EXTREME PREJUDICE.

378
00:27:11,080 --> 00:27:13,280
HE WILL BE, SIR, JUST AS SOON AS WE GET HIS LOCATION FROM FAYED.

379
00:27:13,440 --> 00:27:15,720
IF FAYED CALLS BEFORE I GET BACK, LOOP ME IN. OKAY.

380
00:27:16,560 --> 00:27:17,760
BILL. YEAH?

381
00:27:17,760 --> 00:27:22,400
- I'M SIDELINING CHLOE ON THIS OPERATION. - WHY?

382
00:27:22,760 --> 00:27:25,080
SHE STARTED ASKING QUESTIONS ABOUT JACK.

383
00:27:25,280 --> 00:27:26,640
I... I TRIED PUTTING HER OFF, BUT I...

384
00:27:26,760 --> 00:27:29,400
WHAT DID YOU TELL HER? THE TRUTH.

385
00:27:29,400 --> 00:27:37,880
- I'LL TALK TO HER WHEN I GET THERE. - THANKS.

386
00:27:38,320 --> 00:27:42,320
MOVE OVER. WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

387
00:27:42,600 --> 00:27:44,320
I'M GONNA TRY AND GET A VISUAL ON JACK.

388
00:27:44,680 --> 00:27:46,960
I TOLD YOU, FAYED HAS OUR SURVEILLANCE PROTOCOLS.

389
00:27:46,960 --> 00:27:50,200
HE'S MONITORING FULL-SPECTRUM RADIO, SATELLITE ORBITS AND TRANSMISSIONS.

390
00:27:50,200 --> 00:27:52,360
I HAVE ACCESS TO A SATELLITE THAT'S OFF THE GOVERNMENT GRID.

391
00:27:52,680 --> 00:27:56,000
HOW? I DID A DROP OF WORK FOR THIS ENERGY CONSORTIUM IN UZBEKISTAN.

392
00:27:56,000 --> 00:28:00,520
THEY NEEDED AN ILLEGAL AERIAL SURVEY OF SOME OIL FIELDS. I NEEDED SOME QUICK CASH.

393
00:28:00,640 --> 00:28:01,480
AHA, LOOK.

394
00:28:01,520 --> 00:28:04,360
THE LITTLE BIRD... SHE'S STILL FLYING. SHE'S STILL FLYING.

395
00:28:04,840 --> 00:28:08,800
I THINK I CAN REPOSITION THE CAMERA FROM HERE. MORRIS.

396
00:28:08,800 --> 00:28:10,360
AH, DON'T THANK ME YET, LOVE.

397
00:28:10,840 --> 00:28:43,640
JUST STOP SULKING, AND FIND OUT WHERE BILL BUCHANAN LEFT JACK.

398
00:28:44,120 --> 00:29:09,080
I'VE BEEN WAITING FOR THIS FOR A LONG TIME.

399
00:29:09,080 --> 00:29:13,280
- YES. - THERE IS A PROBLEM. DON'T MOVE OUT OF THE TUNNEL YET.

400
00:29:13,280 --> 00:29:17,600
- WHAT? - I JUST INTERCEPTED A SIGNAL TO A PRIVATELY OWNED SATELLITE.

401
00:29:17,600 --> 00:29:19,400
THERE ARE HUNDREDS OF PRIVATE SATELLITES.

402
00:29:19,440 --> 00:29:22,920
THE SIGNAL IS BEING TRANSMITTED ON A GOVERNMENT FREQUENCY.

403
00:29:22,960 --> 00:29:25,720
THIS SATELLITE... WHAT'S IT LOOKING AT? I CAN'T PINPOINT IT,

404
00:29:25,720 --> 00:29:30,800
BUT THE CAMERA'S BEEN REPOSITIONED TO YOUR SECTOR.

405
00:29:30,880 --> 00:29:32,440
CONNECT ME TO C.T.U.

406
00:29:34,720 --> 00:29:36,320
CHLOE, THIS IS IT. THIS IS IT.

407
00:29:37,360 --> 00:29:39,640
AS SOON AS THE MILITARY HAS ASSAD'S LOCATION,

408
00:29:39,640 --> 00:29:42,640
WE'LL WORK WITH LOCAL LAW ENFORCEMENT TO LIMIT COLLATERAL DAMAGE.

409
00:29:42,640 --> 00:29:44,600
AS MUCH AS WE'RE TRYING TO PREVENT CIVILIAN LOSSES,

410
00:29:44,600 --> 00:29:48,040
OUR PRIORITY IS TO TAKE OUT ASSAD.

411
00:29:48,040 --> 00:29:49,000
FAYED IS ON THE LINE.

412
00:29:50,880 --> 00:29:51,920
THIS IS NADIA YASSIR.

413
00:29:52,080 --> 00:29:57,320
REDIRECT THE SATELLITE YOU HAVE AIMED AT THIS SECTOR.

414
00:29:57,680 --> 00:29:59,200
I DON'T KNOW WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

415
00:29:59,200 --> 00:30:02,640
THEN EXPLAIN THE ACTIVITY ON FREQUENCY ALPHA-0703.

416
00:30:03,720 --> 00:30:05,560
BAUER IS DEAD EITHER WAY,

417
00:30:05,560 --> 00:30:10,000
BUT IF YOU DON'T REDIRECT THAT SATELLITE IN 30 SECONDS, YOU WILL LOSE ASSAD.

418
00:30:10,240 --> 00:30:14,840
I'M TELLING YOU, THERE'S NO SATELLITE. TWENTY-EIGHT SECONDS.

419
00:30:14,840 --> 00:30:18,400
NADIA.

420
00:30:18,960 --> 00:30:20,640
WHERE IS THIS COMING FROM?

421
00:30:20,640 --> 00:30:25,800
INSIDE THE BUILDING. WHERE?

422
00:30:25,880 --> 00:30:30,160
CHLOE'S STATION.

423
00:30:30,240 --> 00:30:32,120
MORRIS. WHAT, LOVE?

424
00:30:32,120 --> 00:30:34,120
REDIRECT THAT SATELLITE.

425
00:30:34,120 --> 00:30:36,840
- REDIRECT THAT SATELLITE. - THE SITUATION IS UNDER CONTROL.

426
00:30:36,840 --> 00:30:38,080
NO, FAYED TAGGED YOUR TRANSMISSION.

427
00:30:38,080 --> 00:30:40,480
WE MAY HAVE LOST OUR ONLY CHANCE AT LOCATING ASSAD.

428
00:30:40,480 --> 00:30:43,800
FAYED, THIS WAS A ROGUE OPERATION. WE'RE REDIRECTING THE SATELLITE NOW.

429
00:30:43,840 --> 00:30:45,320
YOU HAVE 10 SECONDS. MORRIS, DO IT!

430
00:30:45,360 --> 00:30:46,640
NINE. EIGHT. COME ON!

431
00:30:46,840 --> 00:30:48,840
HURRY UP. I'M GOING AS FAST AS I CAN.

432
00:30:48,840 --> 00:30:51,960
SEVEN. SIX. FIVE. FOUR.

433
00:30:52,240 --> 00:30:53,160
IT'S DONE.

434
00:30:55,400 --> 00:30:58,840
IT'S MOVING AWAY, FAYED. THEY REDIRECTED THE SATELLITE.

435
00:30:58,840 --> 00:31:02,280
OTHER CHANNELS? ALL CLEAR.

436
00:31:02,280 --> 00:31:04,400
BECAUSE OF YOUR DECEPTION,

437
00:31:04,400 --> 00:31:07,000
I WILL HAVE TO THINK ABOUT GIVING YOU ASSAD'S LOCATION.

438
00:31:07,400 --> 00:31:08,960
BUT WHAT ABOUT OUR DEAL?

439
00:31:12,920 --> 00:31:14,680
FAYED?

440
00:31:14,800 --> 00:31:29,560
- WE MAY HAVE SPOOKED FAYED. - I HEARD WHAT HAPPENED!

441
00:31:29,560 --> 00:31:30,040
DAMN IT!

442
00:31:30,280 --> 00:31:33,720
WHAT WERE YOU THINKING? IT'S MY FAULT. YOU CAN FIRE ME.

443
00:31:33,720 --> 00:31:37,920
I'D FIRE BOTH OF YOU RIGHT NOW, BUT I CAN'T AFFORD TO LOSE THE MANPOWER. CHLOE.

444
00:31:41,400 --> 00:31:43,080
LOOK AT ME. I'D RATHER NOT, SIR.

445
00:31:43,440 --> 00:31:46,960
LOOK AT ME.

446
00:31:47,520 --> 00:31:51,800
DON'T THINK YOU'RE THE ONLY ONE MOURNING JACK. YOU'RE NOT.

447
00:31:52,080 --> 00:31:55,600
THAT MAY HAVE BEEN OUR ONLY OPTION.

448
00:31:55,840 --> 00:31:59,600
YOU BOTH BETTER HOPE TO GOD YOU DIDN'T JUST BLOW IT.

449
00:31:59,600 --> 00:32:15,360
WE MAY HAVE SACRIFICED JACK FOR NOTHING.

450
00:32:15,520 --> 00:32:25,680
BUCHANAN. BILL, HAVE YOU HEARD FROM FAYED?

451
00:32:25,680 --> 00:32:28,200
- NOT YET. NO. - THE PRESIDENT'S WORRIED.

452
00:32:28,640 --> 00:32:30,720
FAYED SHOULD HAVE CONTACTED US BY NOW.

453
00:32:30,720 --> 00:32:34,600
THERE MAY BE A PROBLEM. THERE'S A POSSIBILITY FAYED'S GOING BACK ON THE DEAL.

454
00:32:34,600 --> 00:32:38,560
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT? HE CAUGHT US TRYING TO TRACK JACK.

455
00:32:38,560 --> 00:32:41,160
THE ORDERS WERE THAT HE WAS TO HAVE A CLEAR FIELD.

456
00:32:41,160 --> 00:32:43,760
I KNOW WHAT THE ORDERS WERE. CHLOE THOUGHT THERE WAS A WORK-AROUND.

457
00:32:43,760 --> 00:32:45,920
SHE DID IT WITHOUT AUTHORIZATION. AW, DAMN IT, BILL!

458
00:32:45,960 --> 00:32:50,160
SHE'S YOUR RESPONSIBILITY. HOW COULD YOU LET THIS HAPPEN? IF WE DON'T TAKE OUT ASSAD...

459
00:32:50,400 --> 00:32:53,680
I DON'T NEED A LECTURE, KAREN. I KNOW WHAT THE STAKES ARE. I DON'T THINK YOU DO.

460
00:32:54,280 --> 00:32:56,880
IF THESE ATTACKS DON'T STOP, THERE ARE PEOPLE IN THIS ADMINISTRATION...

461
00:32:56,880 --> 00:33:01,080
WHO ARE WILLING TO TEAR UP THE CONSTITUTION IN THE NAME OF NATIONAL SECURITY.

462
00:33:01,080 --> 00:33:03,440
THE THINGS THEY'RE TALKING ABOUT DOING...

463
00:33:03,440 --> 00:33:05,880
THIS COUNTRY WILL NEVER RECOVER.

464
00:33:05,880 --> 00:33:10,560
AS SOON AS I HEAR FROM FAYED, YOU'LL BE MY FIRST CALL.

465
00:33:10,560 --> 00:33:14,000
I'M SORRY, BILL. IT'S JUST, I'M...

466
00:33:14,000 --> 00:33:16,440
THERE'S NO NEED TO APOLOGIZE. WE'RE ALL FEELING IT.

467
00:33:17,840 --> 00:33:28,240
I HAVE TO GO.

468
00:33:28,240 --> 00:33:30,040
ANYTHING? IT'S CLEAR.

469
00:33:30,040 --> 00:33:33,280
- ARE YOU SURE? - YES. THEY'RE LEAVING US ALONE.

470
00:33:33,280 --> 00:33:35,760
THE MONEY'S BEEN TRANSFERRED. SHOULD WE CALL C.T.U.?

471
00:33:36,240 --> 00:33:54,800
NOT YET.

472
00:33:54,800 --> 00:34:02,400
YOU NEED TO CALL C.T.U.

473
00:34:20,200 --> 00:34:22,080
I WON'T LET YOU DIE UNTIL I'M READY.

474
00:34:22,800 --> 00:34:24,760
THE CHINESE DIDN'T LEAVE MUCH FOR ME TO WORK WITH.

475
00:34:25,600 --> 00:34:28,760
BUT BEFORE YOU DIE, YOU'RE GOING TO FEEL WHAT MY BROTHER FELT.

476
00:34:30,360 --> 00:34:35,200
I SAW HIS BODY. I KNOW HOW HE DIED.

477
00:34:35,440 --> 00:34:39,920
I KNOW WHAT YOU DID TO HIM.

478
00:34:45,840 --> 00:34:47,120
YOU DON'T NEED ME TO TELL YOU...

479
00:34:47,120 --> 00:35:06,640
THAT THE NERVES ARE BUNDLED HERE.

480
00:35:16,640 --> 00:35:17,080
BETTER.

481
00:35:22,760 --> 00:35:25,840
YOU NEED TO GIVE C.T.U. ASSAD'S LOCATION.

482
00:35:25,920 --> 00:35:28,280
THAT WAS THE DEAL.

483
00:35:28,280 --> 00:35:32,960
ASSAD HAS LOST FAITH IN OUR FIGHT.

484
00:35:33,120 --> 00:35:35,440
HE THINKS OUR TACTICS ARE FAILING.

485
00:35:35,440 --> 00:35:38,600
HE'S BEGUN TALKING ABOUT COMPROMISE,

486
00:35:38,840 --> 00:35:42,280
ABOUT LAYING DOWN OUR ARMS AND NEGOTIATING.

487
00:35:42,960 --> 00:35:46,760
BUT THERE'S NO COMPROMISE, NO NEGOTIATION.

488
00:35:46,760 --> 00:35:51,760
ASSAD IS A TRAITOR.

489
00:35:51,760 --> 00:35:53,680
AND SOON, INSHALLAH,

490
00:35:54,920 --> 00:35:57,960
HE WILL BE DEAD.

491
00:35:58,000 --> 00:35:58,880
THAT'S RIGHT, JACK.

492
00:36:00,720 --> 00:36:04,880
C.T.U. IS ABOUT TO KILL THE WRONG MAN.

493
00:36:04,880 --> 00:36:07,400
ASSAD ISN'T BEHIND THESE ATTACKS.

494
00:36:08,640 --> 00:36:10,280
HE'S COME HERE TO STOP THEM.

495
00:36:11,640 --> 00:36:27,080
HE'S COME HERE TO STOP ME.

496
00:36:34,880 --> 00:36:43,720
YOU WILL DIE FOR NOTHING.

497
00:36:44,000 --> 00:36:46,640
IF FAYED DOESN'T CALL IN FIVE MINUTES, REASSIGN EVERYONE HERE.

498
00:36:46,640 --> 00:36:49,960
IT'S HIM. THIS IS BUCHANAN.

499
00:36:50,080 --> 00:36:52,440
YOU KEPT YOUR END OF THE DEAL. I'LL KEEP MINE.

500
00:36:52,440 --> 00:36:57,600
I'M LISTENING. I HAVE A TRANSPONDER AT ASSAD'S LOCATION.

501
00:36:57,880 --> 00:37:01,960
THIRTY-THREE, 58, 11, NORTH LATITUDE.

502
00:37:01,960 --> 00:37:03,320
THIRTY-THREE, 58, 11.

503
00:37:03,320 --> 00:37:05,160
118, 21, 40, WEST LONGITUDE.

504
00:37:06,760 --> 00:37:09,600
YOU'LL FIND ASSAD THERE.

505
00:37:09,720 --> 00:37:14,440
- WHERE IS THAT? - IT'S COMING.

506
00:37:14,440 --> 00:37:14,920
INGLEWOOD.

507
00:37:15,000 --> 00:37:18,200
HAVE GENERAL BOWEN MOBILIZE THE ATTACK HELICOPTERS. I'LL LET THE PRESIDENT KNOW WE'RE A GO.

508
00:37:18,240 --> 00:37:20,480
CUT OFF FAYED'S ACCESS TO ALL OUR SURVEILLANCE.

509
00:37:20,480 --> 00:37:30,360
I WANNA LOCK DOWN ALL OF OUR SATELLITES. SHUT 'EM DOWN. YOU GOT IT?

510
00:37:31,720 --> 00:37:35,480
WE DID EVERYTHING WE COULD.

511
00:37:36,160 --> 00:37:40,040
I KNOW IT'S TRULY AWFUL, BUT IF IT STOPS THESE ATTACKS,

512
00:37:40,040 --> 00:37:41,160
IT'S FOR THE GREATER GOOD.

513
00:37:42,360 --> 00:38:09,640
THERE'S NO ONE THAT UNDERSTANDS THAT MORE THAN JACK.

514
00:38:09,880 --> 00:38:15,600
DO YOU REMEMBER DOING THIS TO MY BROTHER?

515
00:38:15,640 --> 00:38:16,720
FAYED? WHAT IS IT?

516
00:38:17,280 --> 00:38:30,560
THERE IS A CALL FOR YOU. IT'S IMPORTANT.

517
00:38:40,360 --> 00:38:43,160
YES. THERE'S A PROBLEM.

518
00:38:43,160 --> 00:38:44,160
TELL ME WHAT HAPPENED.

519
00:38:44,160 --> 00:38:48,520
- THE F.B.I... THEY TOOK MY FATHER. - WHERE ARE YOU?

520
00:38:50,840 --> 00:38:52,480
I'M AT A NEIGHBOR'S.

521
00:38:52,480 --> 00:38:54,040
FAYED, YOU KNOW MY FATHER'S INNOCENT.

522
00:38:54,040 --> 00:38:55,400
HE HAS NO IDEA WHAT WE'RE DOING.

523
00:38:55,920 --> 00:38:59,480
IF YOUR FATHER IS MEANT TO BE SACRIFICED,

524
00:38:59,480 --> 00:39:01,640
THAT IS HOW IT WILL BE.

525
00:39:01,640 --> 00:39:42,000
NOW TELL ME WHAT THE F.B.I. SAID.

526
00:39:42,760 --> 00:39:45,920
GOOD. YOU DID THE RIGHT THING.

527
00:39:45,960 --> 00:39:49,120
ARE YOU SURE THE F.B.I. DIDN'T FIND THE PACKAGE?

528
00:39:49,120 --> 00:39:50,280
YES, IT'S WELL HIDDEN.

529
00:39:50,360 --> 00:39:53,280
YOU NEED TO DELIVER IT SOON. I'LL CALL YOU WHEN I HAVE IT.

530
00:39:58,760 --> 00:40:01,480
EVERYTHING OKAY? YEAH, IT WAS JUST MY UNCLE.

531
00:40:01,480 --> 00:40:04,000
HE'S TRYING TO FIND OUT WHERE THEY TOOK MY DAD.

532
00:40:04,000 --> 00:40:06,380
WANNA COME EAT? YEAH.

533
00:40:25,880 --> 00:40:31,000
GET IN THERE!

534
00:40:31,200 --> 00:40:32,500
FIND HIM!

